&lt;div&gt;&lt;iframe loading=&quot;lazy&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;music.berdandy.com&#x2F;souls-beat-slow-single&#x2F;embed&#x2F;1&#x2F;&quot; style=&quot;min-width: 480px;&quot; title=&quot;Audio player widget for &amp;quot;Souls Beat Slow&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can listen to the whole show at &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.audiointerface.org&#x2F;shows&#x2F;nham-mixtapes&#x2F;20250301&#x2F;&quot;&gt;audiointerface.org&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, and I definitely recommend it. There&#x27;s some good stuff in there.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
