    <entry xml:lang="en">
        <title>Leatherworking Shop Space</title>
        <published>2025-01-25T00:00:00+00:00</published>
        <updated>2025-01-25T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
        
        <author>
          <name>
            
              Unknown
            
          </name>
        </author>
        
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://berdandy.com/blog/shopspace/"/>
        <id>https://berdandy.com/blog/shopspace/</id>
        
        <content type="html" xml:base="https://berdandy.com/blog/shopspace/">&lt;p&gt;I&#x27;m increasingly feeling limited by my need to unpack and repack my leatherworking tools and materials when I
somehow excavate some time and energy from my life -- and the competition for the dining room table is fierce.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a result, I&#x27;m staking out some space in the basement for a multipurpose workspace.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;the-plan&quot;&gt;The Plan&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&quot;&quot; type=&quot;checkbox&quot; checked=&quot;&quot;&#x2F;&gt;
Reorganize existing woodworking tools&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&quot;&quot; type=&quot;checkbox&quot; checked=&quot;&quot;&#x2F;&gt;
Move some tools to open up cluttered workbench for heavy stuff (hammering, stitching chisels, etc)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&quot;&quot; type=&quot;checkbox&quot; checked=&quot;&quot;&#x2F;&gt;
Get&#x2F;build a second workbench for wet stuff (dying, painting, etc)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&quot;&quot; type=&quot;checkbox&quot; checked=&quot;&quot;&#x2F;&gt;
Bins &amp;amp; storage for leatherworking scraps and consumables&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&quot;&quot; type=&quot;checkbox&quot; checked=&quot;&quot;&#x2F;&gt;
Make large material storage (rolled in cardboard concrete forms)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;bonus-ideas&quot;&gt;Bonus Ideas&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&quot;&quot; type=&quot;checkbox&quot; checked=&quot;&quot;&#x2F;&gt;
Move guest room TV&#x2F;speakers to shop&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&quot;&quot; type=&quot;checkbox&quot;&#x2F;&gt;
Small photography area using unused basement furniture&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Getting there...&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
